Package zserio.runtime.io

This package contains stream manipulation classes.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    BitStreamReader
    An interface for a bit stream reader implementation.
    BitStreamWriter
    An interface for a bit stream writer implementation.
    InitializeOffsetsWriter Deprecated
    This interface has been moved to the Writer interface.
    PackableWriter
    Interface for writing to bit stream for packable classes generated by Zserio.
    Writer
    Interface for writing to bit stream for classes generated by Zserio.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BitBuffer
    Class which holds any bit sequence.
    ByteArrayBitStreamReader
    A bit stream reader using byte array.
    ByteArrayBitStreamWriter
    A bit stream writer using byte array.
    SerializeUtil
    Provides help methods for serialization and deserialization of generated objects.
